** README **

For full instructions on how to install kmotion check out the docs directory. 
There is an odf (OpenOffice format) document and a PDF.

If you find any errors or omissions please email me at dave6502@googlemail.com

Cheers

Dave

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
** NOTE **

If you downloaded kmotion from svn you will have to 'sudo chmod +x ./install.py'
GoogleCode seems to have a hang up about letting 'install.py' be executable !
